<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Total Control — Unlock a smarter worksite</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/landing.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="container topbar-inner">
      <span class="cs-phone">Customer Service: 844.873.4948</span>
      <nav class="topbar-links">
        <a href="#" class="lang">EN</a>
        <a href="/login">Sign In</a>
        <span class="dot">·</span>
        <a href="/register">Register</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <header class="mainnav">
    <div class="container mainnav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Total Control home">
        <span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">TC</span>
        <span class="brand-text">Total Control<sup>®</sup></span>
      </a>
      <nav class="primary-nav" aria-label="Primary">
        <a href="#">Rent</a>
        <a href="#">Buy</a>
        <a href="#" class="active">Total Control</a>
        <a href="#">Invoices &amp; Payments</a>
        <a href="#">Locations</a>
        <a href="#">Solutions</a>
        <a href="#">Services</a>
      </nav>
      <a href="/login" class="cta-button">Sign In</a>
      <a href="/register" class="cta-button cta-button--secondary">Register</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="kicker">Total Control<sup>®</sup></p>
        <h1>Unlock a smarter worksite today.</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          Real-time visibility into your fleet, your projects, and your costs — across every site,
          from one platform built for the way you actually work.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta-row">
          <a href="/login" class="cta-button cta-button--lg">Sign In</a>
          <a href="/register" class="ghost-button cta-button--lg">Register</a>
          <a href="#features" class="ghost-button cta-button--lg">Learn More</a>
        </div>
        <p class="trust-line">Trusted by leading GCs &amp; specialty contractors across North America</p>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="hero-card-head">
            <span class="dot-row"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span>
            <span class="hero-card-title">Fleet Overview</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-card-stat">
            <span class="stat-num">94<small>%</small></span>
            <span class="stat-label">Utilization · last 7 days</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-card-bar"><i style="width:88%"></i></div>
          <div class="hero-card-bar"><i style="width:62%"></i></div>
          <div class="hero-card-bar"><i style="width:73%"></i></div>
          <div class="hero-card-bar"><i style="width:45%"></i></div>
          <div class="hero-card-foot">
            <span>Optimized · 412 assets</span>
            <span class="badge">LIVE</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="features" class="features-band">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="kicker kicker--center">More Control. Less Effort.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Next-gen features built for the worksite</h2>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <article class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill="currentColor" d="M19.43 12.98a7.97 7.97 0 0 0 0-1.96l2.04-1.58a.5.5 0 0 0 .12-.64l-1.93-3.34a.5.5 0 0 0-.6-.22l-2.4.96a8.06 8.06 0 0 0-1.7-.98l-.36-2.55a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.43h-3.86a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.43l-.36 2.55c-.6.25-1.17.58-1.7.98l-2.4-.96a.5.5 0 0 0-.6.22L2.95 8.8a.5.5 0 0 0 .12.64l2.04 1.58a8.07 8.07 0 0 0 0 1.96L3.07 14.56a.5.5 0 0 0-.12.64l1.93 3.34c.13.22.4.31.62.22l2.4-.96c.53.4 1.1.73 1.7.98l.36 2.55c.04.24.25.43.5.43h3.86c.25 0 .46-.19.5-.43l.36-2.55c.6-.25 1.17-.58 1.7-.98l2.4.96c.22.09.49 0 .62-.22l1.93-3.34a.5.5 0 0 0-.12-.64l-2.04-1.58zM12 15.5A3.5 3.5 0 1 1 12 8.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Optimize Operations</h3>
          <p>Track utilization in real time and right-size your fleet to the job — no more idle assets billing by the day.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill="currentColor" d="M3 13h2v-2H3v2zm0 4h2v-2H3v2zm0-8h2V7H3v2zm4 4h14v-2H7v2zm0 4h14v-2H7v2zM7 7v2h14V7H7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Enhance Productivity</h3>
          <p>Spot bottlenecks before they cost you. Coordinate teams across sites without the back-and-forth.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill="currentColor" d="M3.5 18.5l6-6 4 4L22 6.92 20.59 5.5l-7.09 8.08-4-4L2 17l1.5 1.5z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Forecast Costs</h3>
          <p>Project run-rate and lifetime cost on every contract. No more month-end surprises in the finance review.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill="currentColor" d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.4 9.74 8 11 4.6-1.26 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3zm0 18.93C8.52 19.93 6 15.97 6 12V6.39l6-2.25 6 2.25V12c0 3.97-2.52 7.93-6 8.93z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Reduce Risk</h3>
          <p>Built-in compliance, certificate alerts, and emissions tracking keep every job audit-ready, every day.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="capabilities">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="kicker kicker--center kicker--light">The Total Control loop</p>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title--light">See. Manage. Measure. Optimize.</h2>
      <div class="capability-grid">
        <div class="cap-card">
          <span class="cap-num">01</span>
          <h3>See</h3>
          <p>Live map of every asset across every site — indoor and outdoor, owned and rented.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-card">
          <span class="cap-num">02</span>
          <h3>Manage</h3>
          <p>Reassign, swap, off-rent, and request service in a few clicks. No phone tag with the yard.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-card">
          <span class="cap-num">03</span>
          <h3>Measure</h3>
          <p>Custom dashboards on utilization, idle time, fuel burn, hours, and contract status.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-card">
          <span class="cap-num">04</span>
          <h3>Optimize</h3>
          <p>Recommendations that translate live data into bottom-line savings, week over week.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="value-props">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vp-grid">
        <div class="vp">
          <h3>Easy to use</h3>
          <p>Designed for foremen and field crews — not just back-office analysts. Onboarding takes minutes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vp">
          <h3>Cost forecasting</h3>
          <p>Project, lifetime, and per-asset cost models you can trust at the bid table and at the close.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vp">
          <h3>Customizable</h3>
          <p>Build the views your teams actually use. Share them across an org in a single click.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="testimonial-band">
    <div class="container">
      <blockquote>
        <p>&ldquo;Total Control gave us 17% more equipment utilization in a single quarter &mdash; and saved our PMs hours every week.&rdquo;</p>
        <footer>— VP of Operations, top-25 GC</footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faqs">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <details>
        <summary>What does Total Control include?</summary>
        <p>Real-time fleet visibility, custom reports, project-level cost rollups, configurable alerts, and a companion mobile app — all in a single sign-on experience.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How do I sign in?</summary>
        <p>Click <a href="/login">Sign In</a> in the header if you already have an account, or <a href="/register">Register</a> to create one. Your session is secured via your organization's identity provider — no separate password to remember.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Is mobile supported?</summary>
        <p>Yes. The web platform is fully responsive, and we ship native iOS and Android apps for the field.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I integrate with my ERP?</summary>
        <p>Yes — Total Control exposes a documented REST API and pre-built connectors for the most common back-office systems.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container cta-band-inner">
      <h2>Ready to take control?</h2>
      <p>Sign in to your account or get registered in minutes.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:0.9rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="/login" class="cta-button cta-button--lg">Sign In</a>
        <a href="/register" class="ghost-button cta-button--lg">Register</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container footer-cols">
      <div>
        <h4>Equipment</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">Rent</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Buy</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Service</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Solutions</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">Total Control</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Mobile App</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Lien Waivers</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Company</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">Careers</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Investors</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">News</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Support</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Locations</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">844.873.4948</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container footer-bottom">
      <span>&copy; Total Control demo. SAML SP-initiated SSO test app for local development.</span>
      <span class="meta-detail">
        SP entity: <code><%= spEntityId %></code> ·
        ACS: <code><%= callbackUrl %></code> ·
        <a href="/saml/metadata">metadata</a>
      </span>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
